snippet: Manchester United manager Louis van Gaal said his team need to learn to cope with pressure after they slumped to a 2-1 home defeat to Swansea City on the opening day of the Premier League season....

headline.print_headline: United Need to Learn to Cope With Pressure Says Van Gaal
headline.main: United Need to Learn to Cope With Pressure Says Van Gaal

lead_paragraph: Manchester United manager Louis van Gaal said his team need to learn to cope with pressure after they slumped to a 2-1 home defeat to Swansea City on the opening day of the Premier League season.
